latestPosts.caption:
If you have a dream, wake up, make it a goal 
I have always been fascinated by fashion industry since my teenage. 
Coming from a service class family, like any other mentality of “padhoge likhoge bnoge NAWAB” I pursued my studies and qualified as a GIS Analyst in a MNC. 

It is true education gives you ultimate confidence.

Finding a career that would not only be fulfilling, interesting and rewarding was the main thought of shifting to Makeup Industry. 

Younger me would be so proud for having this journey and turning my ultimate passion into career. 
.
